<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV90">
<l>kulaṅkaḷāya vīriraṇṭi loṉṟilumpi ṟantilēṉ</l>
<l>nalaṅkaḷāya naṟkalaikaḷ nāvilunna viṉṟilēṉ</l>
<l>pulaṉkaḷaintum veṉṟilēṉpo ṟiyilēṉpu ṉitaniṉ</l>
<l>ilaṅkupāta maṉṟimaṟṟor paṟṟilēṉem mīcaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I was not born in any of the four castes.</l>
<l>I have not learned the four good Vedas flourishing with goodness.</l>
<l>I, a senseless person, have not conquered the five senses.</l>
<l>O Pure [Lord]! I have not embraced anything other than</l>
<l rend="indent">Your lustrous feet, O our Supreme Being!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
